.TH criticalstat 8  "2018-06-07" "USER COMMANDS"
.SH NAME
criticalstat \- A tracer to find and report long atomic critical sections in kernel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B criticalstat [\-h] [\-p] [\-i] [\-d DURATION]
.SH DESCRIPTION

